Type: Package
Package: MRHLP
Title: Multiple Regression Model with a Hidden Logistic Process ('MRHLP') for Joint Segmentation of Multivariate Time Series
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Faicel", "Chamroukhi", role = c("aut"),
    email = "faicel.chamroukhi@unicaen.fr",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5894-3103")),
    person("Marius", "Bartcus", role = c("aut"), 
    email = "marius.bartcus@gmail.com"),
    person("Florian", "Lecocq", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "florian.lecocq@outlook.com"))
Description: Flexible and user-friendly probabilistic joint segmentation of 
    multivariate time series with smooth and/or abrupt regime changes by a 
    mixture model-based multiple regression approach with a hidden logistic 
    process, fitted by the EM algorithm. See also the packages 'MHMMR' and 
    'RHLP'.
URL: https://github.com/fchamroukhi/MRHLP
